            </g></svg></span>
            <span><a href="tel:+18773777172" class="hover:text-primary transition duration-300">877-377-7172</a> &mdash; Reservations & Quotes</span>
          </p>

          <p class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><svg id='Phone_24' width='23' height='23' viewBox='0 0 24 24' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'><rect width='24' height='24' stroke='none' fill='#000000' opacity='0'/>
            <g transform="matrix(0.87 0 0 0.87 12 12)" >
